{
  "stem": "25809.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had a lot of fun till Rabbi Prins felt I was getting too powerful and too popular and literally kicked me out of the synagogue because he didn't like the way things were developing.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was getting so popular and getting a little bit rowdy also.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he felt it was getting out of hand, so he stopped the dances.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By then, I was about to leave for Australia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was-- by now, I was 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't finish that school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got kicked out of school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, my father was very happy when Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Holtzup ?], the-- the principal of the school-- I went to first year of HBO, a second year of HBO, and then I had to repeat it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the third year, my-- my marks or my figures were so bad that he said, I don't want you in this school anymore.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You better get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I really don't need people like you here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Little did he know that I had great difficulties in studying at that point in time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had great difficulties at home, where there were continuous fights and-- and-- and arguments, and I couldn't concentrate.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just couldn't concentrate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the fact that I could concentrate when it was necessary is because when I came back 10 years later, I had to get a [DUTCH] diploma in order to run my mother's store, and I took some private-- private lessons.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in eight, nine months I went through the whole course that a lot of people sometimes take two or three years and went through it, like you would say, cum laude, with-- with As and Bs.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So yeah, given the right atmosphere, I had no difficulties in studying.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
